Rilmani exist to protect the middle ground and correct any imbalances that would compromise it. Aurumachs are the leaders of the Rilmani. They are ogre-sized, golden skinned diplomats who first use their words in affairs of balance, but are equally capable warriors. 

      Sources:&nbsp;
    
            
                    Planescape Monstrous Compendium Appendix II        
              
                    Fiend Folio (D&amp;D 3.4)